*****************************************************************************
* REGISTER ******************************************************************
*****************************************************************************

@Node "How_to_Register" "Cybertracker.guide/How to Register"
@Toc "Main"


 @{u}@{b}How To Register@{uu}@{ub}

  1. Print out the "Cybertracker Registration Form". The registration
     form can be found in the docs drawer.

  2. Please print or write LEGIBLY...

       a. Fill in your name and mailing address.

       b. Your fidonet or e-mail address (not required, but if present
          you will automatically be notified when your copy of the
          keyfile is shipping).

       c. Your private voice telephone number (not compulsory). If
          possible, use the form "+12-(13)-123456", where 12 is the
          country code and 13 is the area code.

  3. Tick...

       a. Decide how to transfer the money. Cash (at your own risk), a
          postal money order is suggested. Foreign checks are *NOT*
          accepted!

       b. Decide what way you would like to get keyfile.

  4. Send the registration form to a registration site, currently
     to Andreas Öman (developer).

		Andreas Öman
		Olebyn Olofsberg
		S-67191 ARVIKA
		Sweden

  5. Wait for your key to be delivered. Thank you for registering!
     You should receive your key within ten days after the arrival of
     your registration fee. But please allow up to eight weeks for
     delivery, due to unforseen circumstances.

  6. A keyfile is proof of the personal license you have to use
     Cybertracker. You are not allowed to sell or give away the keyfile.

@EndNode

