@Node "Program_History" "Cybertracker.guide/Program_History"
@Toc "Main"


 @{u}@{b}Program History@{uu}@{ub}


 @{u}@{b}Version 0.67@{uu}@{ub}

  Some major bug fixes.

 @{u}@{b}Version 0.70@{uu}@{ub}

   * Cybertracker now supports @{" Fpl " Link Fpl_scripts}. 

   * This Doc :)

   * GUI rearranged.

   * New configuration abilities.

   * Cybertracker crashes alot, many errors corrected.

   * Crash fixes are also corrected in SampleEd and FourierLab.

   * Midi Support (still under development)   

   * Option G (Gunnar mode) requested by user #3. This is a palette
     preferable to use with digital monitors.


@EndNode

